# Enterprise Multi-Agent AI Assistant — Implementation Plan v2

## Current State → Target State

| Dimension | Current (Medium RAG) | Target (Enterprise) |
|---|---|---|
| Pipeline | 3 nodes: retrieve → grade → generate | 13-stage deep pipeline |
| Retrieval | Vector-only (ChromaDB MMR) | Hybrid: Vector + BM25 with re-ranking |
| Memory | None (stateless) | SQLite-persisted sessions + conversation history |
| Auth | None | API-key based auth middleware |
| Safety | None | Guardrails + hallucination check + citation verification |
| Search | Static KB only | KB + user-uploaded docs + Tavily web fallback |
