## Proposed Changes — Detailed

### Phase 1 — Pipeline State & Graph Foundation

#### [NEW] `app/pipeline/state.py`
A single `PipelineState` TypedDict flows through all 13 nodes. Key fields:

```python
class PipelineState(TypedDict):
    # Input
    raw_query: str
    session_id: str
    user_id: str
    api_key: str
    
    # Auth & Validation
    is_authenticated: bool
    is_valid_query: bool
    validation_error: str | None
    
    # Classification & Rewriting
    intent: str           # "rag" | "debug" | "codegen" | "concept"
    rewritten_queries: list[str]  # expanded query variants
    
    # Retrieval
    retrieved_docs: list[Document]
    bm25_docs: list[Document]
    web_docs: list[Document]      # Tavily results
    user_docs: list[Document]     # from uploaded documents
    
    # Post-retrieval
    reranked_docs: list[Document]
    compressed_context: str
    retrieval_score: float        # overall confidence score
    
    # Generation
    can_answer: bool              # hallucination pre-check result
    generation: str
    citations: list[dict]         # verified source references
    is_safe: bool                 # guardrails result
    
    # Metadata (for UI trace panel)
    pipeline_trace: list[dict]    # [{node, latency_ms, status}]
    response_id: str              # UUID for feedback linking
    confidence: str               # "high" | "medium" | "low"
    
    # Memory
    conversation_history: list[dict]
```

#### [NEW] `app/pipeline/graph.py`
- Assembles all 13 nodes into a `StateGraph`
- Adds conditional edges: if `is_authenticated=False` → route to error response
- If `is_valid_query=False` → route to error response
- If `can_answer=False` → skip generation, trigger Tavily fallback
- If `is_safe=False` → block response, return safety message
- Compiles to a `CompiledGraph` singleton

